  <header class="header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-txt">
        <h1>Clinical Narratives</h1>
        <p>
          Clinical narratives hold vast amounts of hidden insights within medical text. They provide essential details
          on treatments, medications, and patient history. Unlocking this knowledge through NLP empowers healthcare
          professionals to access accurate, structured, and meaningful information with ease.
        </p>
        <div class="button">
          <button>
            <a href="/user-search">
              Get Started
            </a>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img class="header-img" src="/images/index-img.jpg" />
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="boxes">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>FEATURES</h1>
      <div class="box-container">
        <div class="box">
          <h2>OCR Scanning</h2>
          <img src="/flaticons/index/ocr.png" />
          <p>
            Our system transforms handwritten or printed prescriptions into digital text. By automating this process, it
            reduces human error and ensures important details such as drug names and dosages are captured effectively.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
          <h2>Machine Learning</h2>
          <img src="/flaticons/index/coding.png" />
          <p>
            The system leverages BioBERT NER to accurately detect medicine names within clinical text. After
            identification, it retrieves detailed information such as dosages, drug relations, and prices, transforming
            unstructured data into meaningful medical insights.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
          <h2>Medical Insights</h2>
          <img src="/flaticons/index/documents.png" />
          <p>
            Extracted information is structured into clear, readable outputs. This enables healthcare professionals to
            quickly access drug details, side effects, and relations, supporting safer prescribing and faster
            decision-making.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="f-1">
